revision.text: ==English== {{wikipedia}} ===Etymology=== Borrowed from {{bor|en|qu|-}}. ===Noun=== {{en-noun|s|yanakuna}} # {{lb|en|historical}} An individual in the [[Inca]] [[empire|Empire]] who left the [[ayllu]] system and worked full-time at a variety of tasks for the Inca, their [[queen]]{{,}} or the [[religious]] [[establishment]].
